---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Jeff Melton - DevOps & Platform Engineering Consultant">
    <style>
        /* Custom gradient for hero section */
        .hero-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }

    </style>

    <section class="hero-gradient text-white py-16 text-center" id="home">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">DevOps & Platform Engineering Consultant</h1>
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-8 opacity-90 max-w-4xl mx-auto">I work across the entire problem-solving lifecycleâ€”from identifying systemic issues that span multiple domains, to designing comprehensive solutions that address root causes, to building and implementing the technical platforms that make those solutions sustainable.</p>
            <a href="#case-studies" class="inline-block bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">See My Work</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" id="what-i-do">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-slate-700">What I Do</h2>
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                <p class="text-lg mb-6 px-4 sm:px-8 text-left">I help organizations scale and optimize their technology stack, improving outcomes by designing and implementing solutions that automate complexity away. My background spans both hands-on technical implementation and enterprise business operations, so I understand both what's technically possible and what actually works in your organizational context.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50" id="case-studies">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-slate-700">Case Studies</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-4"><a href="/case-studies/legacy-infrastructure-modernization" class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">Infrastructure Modernization</a></h3>
                    <p class="text-base">Transformed a major retailer's technology stack across 600+ locations, delivering <strong>$2M+ in cost savings</strong> while maintaining business continuity. Achieved <strong>150:1 operational efficiency</strong> and zero-downtime migrations through strategic planning and phased implementation.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-4"><a href="/case-studies/platform-engineering" class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">Operational Excellence at Scale</a></h3>
                    <p class="text-base">Built enterprise automation platform that eliminated weeks of manual work, delivering <strong>$400K+ annual cost avoidance</strong> and reclaiming <strong>2000+ engineering hours yearly</strong>. Reduced critical operational cycles from days to minutes across 6000+ systems.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-4"><a href="/case-studies/strategic-architecture" class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">Strategic Technology Planning</a></h3>
                    <p class="text-base">Guided enterprise architecture decisions for 600+ locations, balancing emerging technology requirements with budget constraints and vendor relationships. Delivered comprehensive analysis that informed <strong>multi-million dollar infrastructure investments</strong> and strategic planning cycles.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center mt-12 p-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-4">My Philosophy</h3>
                <p class="italic text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg">
                    "Technology should accelerate business growth, not constrain it. I work with your existing teams and processes to identify opportunities for automation and optimization that deliver measurable results without disrupting operations."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>